// __NAME__ Agent — BOF Loader (adaptix_default)
//
// Realistic BOF (Beacon Object File) loader for the Rust implant template.
// Scope is intentionally explicit:
//   - Windows only
//   - x64 COFF objects only
//   - synchronous execution, with async routed through the same path for now
//
// This mirrors the validated C++ loader override instead of depending on
// Cobalt-Strike-specific client-side bootstrap tricks from Rust-authored BOF
// PoCs. In other words: useful, bounded, and less haunted.

